query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 10 AND q.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('accessibility',
'android',
'apache-flex',
'azure-storage',
'babeljs',
'gson',
'macros',
'migration',
'selector',
'sftp',
'sql-update',
'twilio',
'typo3',
'ubuntu-14.04',
'version-control');
